What do u think of {{champion:1}} since the last buff ?

I'm rather puzzled that Jhin would even be considered the innate problem when Hail of Blades is the thing that launched the whole situation in the first place. If you'd ask me, Hail of Blades is a rune that needs work on because : 

- It's very rarely used by other champions (only Rek'Sai comes to mind, even though she hasn't been meta in a long time);
- It coincides in purpose to Lethal Tempo, even though HoB would find  more benefits in the Precision tree instead of Domination.  Jhin having very limited usable runes in the rest of the minor runes (running Taste of Blood, Eyeball collection and Ravenous Hunter) shows weakness in options. Perhaps replace lethal tempo by Hail of Blades and make further changes from there?
